OL,3,CThree people with incurable conditions
OL,4,Cshare views on assisted dying
OL,6,FAhead of the political debate on
OL,7,Fwhether should legalise assisted
OL,8,Fdying, I have been speaking to three
OL,9,Fresidents with incurable conditions.
OL,11,FThey would all potentially be eligible
OL,12,Funder the proposed law to end their
OL,13,Flives but each has a different view
OL,14,Fabout whether that is a choice they
OL,15,Fwant.
OL,17,FHere are their stories...
OL,19,FLynne Cottignies
