OL,3,CThree people with incurable conditions
OL,4,Cshare views on assisted dying
OL,6,FI first met Lynne weeks before at her
OL,7,Fhouse in Jersey.
OL,9,FThe sun shone on her and her family as
OL,10,Fwe talked about assisted dying.
OL,12,F"At least that way you could arrange
OL,13,Fit, you could have a definite date,
OL,14,Fyou could make sure that the people
OL,15,Fyou want there are with you", she
OL,16,Fsaid, taking a moment to clear a tear
OL,17,Ffrom her eye.
OL,19,F"That's all I'm asking really, for my
OL,20,Ffamily to be there with me."
