OL,3,CThree people with incurable conditions
OL,4,Cshare views on assisted dying
OL,6,FLynne's daughter lives in Jersey but
OL,7,Fher son is based in Canada and she
OL,8,Fcouldn't know whether he would be
OL,9,Fthere at the end.
OL,11,F"To have that choice and choose who
OL,12,Fwill be there at the time is a basic
OL,13,Fright," Lynne said.
OL,15,FJames Bedding
OL,17,FJames Bedding lives life to the full.
OL,19,FHe is a business owner and a qualified
OL,20,Fdrone pilot.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
