OL,3,CThree people with incurable conditions
OL,4,Cshare views on assisted dying
OL,6,FBut at the age of 15, he fell off a
OL,7,Fsea wall and broke his spinal cord.
OL,9,FHe is paralysed from the neck down and
OL,10,Fsees assisted dying as something he
OL,11,Fmay want when he is decades older.
OL,13,F"I wouldn't want to get to the age
OL,14,Fwhere I may be in my 70s or 80s
OL,15,Fsuffering in a bed, struggling to
OL,16,Fbreathe and literally waiting to die,"
OL,17,Fhe explained.
OL,19,F"For me to have the end of life in
OL,20,Fplace is extremely important, to have
OL,21,Fthat choice for peace of mind."
