OL,3,CThree people with incurable conditions
OL,4,Cshare views on assisted dying
OL,6,FJames may be eligible for an assisted
OL,7,Fdeath in the future under 'Route Two',
OL,8,Fwhich allows for those with incurable
OL,9,Fphysical conditions and in "unbearable
OL,10,Fsuffering" to access the service.
OL,12,FHe said his perfect final day, if he
OL,13,Fhad an assisted death, would be "to be
OL,14,Fwith my friends and my family and my
OL,15,Fdearest around me."
OL,17,FMartin O'Neill
OL,19,FBut not all people with incurable
OL,20,Fconditions support assisted dying or
OL,21,Fassisted suicide.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
