OL,3,CThree people with incurable conditions
OL,4,Cshare views on assisted dying
OL,6,FIn 2014, Martin O'Neill had a mesh
OL,7,Fimplant surgery that left him in daily
OL,8,Fagony and permanently disabled.
OL,10,FHad assisted dying been available at
OL,11,Fthe worst times, he says he "wouldn't
OL,12,Fbe here".
OL,14,F"When someone comes in with a chronic
OL,15,Fillness and they're suffering, we
OL,16,Fcan't turn round and say it's fine
OL,17,Fbecause we're going to give you
OL,18,Fmedicine to die," he told me.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
