OL,3,CThree people with incurable conditions
OL,4,Cshare views on assisted dying
OL,6,F"We should be instilling hope when
OL,7,Fpeople are sick and they say the only
OL,8,Fhope I've got is to die. What message
OL,9,Fdoes that send?
OL,11,F"Everyone deserves dignity in death
OL,12,F... but we cannot condemn humanity by
OL,13,Fkilling people through compassion.
OL,14,FIt's moronic, it's madness."
OL,16,FThey have all made their case, now
OL,17,Fit's the turn of Jersey States Members
OL,18,Fto have their say.
